node.text:
The United States Marine Corps operate two STOVL (Short Take Off Vertical Landing) aircraft. The McDonnell Douglas (now Boeing) AV-8B Harrier II and the new Lockheed Martin F-35B Lightning II. Both are extremely capable aircraft which is your favorite?! Presented in conjunction with This is Flight! 
#thisisflight #AirshowStuff #av8b #f35 #f35b #stovl #harrier #usmc #lightningii #mcasyuma

node.text:
Some awesome footage from  @gkblackteam this weekend in Decatur, IL. 
@robholland5150 getting a good view of the @armygoldenknights jump ship before he circles the jumpers to kick off the show! 

Yesterday the Black Demonstration Team had the privilege of sharing the skies with champion pilot @robholland5150 ✈️
Thank you for the experience and we look forward to flying with you more this weekend, Rob! 

Make sure to check us out at the Decatur Airshow today and tomorrow as we jump in 😎🪂

node.text:
Great to still see Balley's Bomber still coming to EAA - The Spirit of Aviation  AirVenture! 
In case you haven't seen it before it's a 1/3 B-17 Flying Fortress that is flown with a pilot on board!
Crew: 1
Length: 24 ft (7.3 m)
Wingspan: 34 ft 7 in (10.54 m)
Powerplant: 4 × Hirth F-30 Two cycle piston, 85 hp (63 kW) each
Propellers: 3-bladed

#balleysbomber #b17flyingfortress #eaa #airventure #osh21 #airventure #3000thpost
